   The structure is composed of 7 blocks.  There are three layers.  The arrangement is asymmetrical.  Two vertical, green rectangular prisms are placed on either side of a central, taller, orange cylindrical block. Atop the cylinder is a triangular orange block. Two orange triangular blocks rest on the bottom layer, on either side of the central structure, adjacent to the green rectangular prisms.
